gement, LLC., is a leveraged ETF that aims to deliver 3 times the daily performance of</span></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/498381212/image_498381212.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741639-dfen-too-risky-right-now", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 09:58:03"}, {"id": "4741638", "title": "Arcos Dorados Costs Are Delevering, Not A Great Sign, Maintain Hold", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458464593/image_458464593.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt='Iluminado restaurante McDonald\"s al atardecer' data-id=\"458464593\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1020px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458464593/image_458464593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458464593/image_458464593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458464593/image_458464593.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458464593/image_458464593.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458464593/image_458464593.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458464593/image_458464593.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458464593/image_458464593.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458464593/image_458464593.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">sshepard/iStock Unreleased via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Arcos Dorados (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ARCO\" title=\"Arcos Dorados Holdings Inc.\">ARCO</a></span>) released 3Q24 earnings.</p> <p>The company's operations are still growing, with challenges only in Argentina, which is undergoing a deep recession. On the other hand, growth does not seem to be pushing margins up anymore.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458464593/image_458464593.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741638-arcos-dorados-costs-are-delevering-not-a-great-sign-maintain-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 09:11:32"}, {"id": "4741637", "title": "NAD Vs. NXP Revisited: Time To Delever", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"On the table are pie charts, a pen and a folder with the inscription - Municipal bond.\" data-id=\"1253600459\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Dzmitry Skazau</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Leveraged Funds Outperform In 2024 But Dividend Hikes May Have Been The Reason</h2> <p>It's been a year since I first <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4656162-nad-vs-nxp-leverage-quality-and-duration-in-muni-bond-funds\">compared leveraged and unleveraged municipal bond closed-end funds</a> using two examples from <a href=\"https://www.nuveen.com/en-us/closed-end-funds?assetclass=Municipal%20fixed%20income%20-%20National%20-%20High%20yield|||Municipal%20fixed%20income%20-%20National%20-%20Investment%20grade|||Municipal%20fixed%20income%20-%20National%20-%20Investment%20grade%20/%20high%20yield\" rel=\"nofollow\">Nuveen</a>. Leveraged funds were</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253600459/image_1253600459.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741637-nad-vs-nxp-revisited-time-to-delever", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 09:07:33"}, {"id": "4741636", "title": "BigCommerce Holdings: Growing E-Commerce Venture At A Cheap Price", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young woman doing online shopping for clothes on smartphone at home\" data-id=\"1814678203\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Images By Tang Ming Tung</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Shares of BigCommerce Holdings (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BIGC\" title=\"BigCommerce Holdings, Inc.\">BIGC</a></span>) have surged after the e-Commerce company submitted <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BIGC/earnings\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/BIGC/earnings\" target=\"_blank\">better than expected</a> third fiscal quarter earnings in November. BigCommerce has seen a post-pandemic slowdown in its revenue growth, but the e-Commerce platform continues to have traction in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1814678203/image_1814678203.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741636-bigcommerce-holdings-growing-e-commerce-venture-at-a-cheap-price", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 08:58:55"}, {"id": "4741632", "title": "Vigil Neuroscience: Down On A Competitor's Failure", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Medicine costs concept\" data-id=\"1886168190\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>The stock of Vigil Neuroscience (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VIGL\" title=\"Vigil Neuroscience, Inc.\">VIGL</a></span>) has been through a rough patch lately, having shed about a quarter of its value following a readout of Alector\u2019s competitor drug AL002.</p> <p>Vigil Neuroscience is focused on targeting microglia, one</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1886168190/image_1886168190.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741632-vigil-neuroscience-down-on-competitors-failure", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 08:44:07"}, {"id": "4740932", "title": "Politics And The Markets 12/03/24", "description": "<p><span>This is the forum for daily political discussion on Seeking Alpha. A new version is published every market day.</span></p> <p>Please don't leave political comments on other articles or posts on the site.</p> <p>The comments below are not regulated with the same rigor as the rest of the site, and this is an <strong>'enter at your own risk' </strong>area as discussion can get very heated. If you can't stand the heat... you know what they say...</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>More on Today's Markets:</span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span></span></b></p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b>Moderation Guidelines:</b></p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"><b><span></span></b>We remove comments under the following categories:</p> <ul> <li>Personal attacks on another user account</li> <li>Anti-Vaxxer or covid related misinformation</li> <li>Stereotyping, prejudiced or racist language about individuals or the topic under discussion.</li> <li>Inciting violence messages, encouraging hate groups and political violence.</li> </ul> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">Regardless of which side of the political divide you find yourself, please be courteous and don't direct abuse at other users.</p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\">For any issue with regards to comments please email us at : moderation@seekingalpha.com.</p> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span>Seeking Alpha's Disclosure:</span></b><span> Past performance is no guarantee of future results. No recommendation or advice is being given as to whether any investment is suitable for a particular investor. Any views or opinions expressed above may not reflect those of Seeking Alpha as a whole. Seeking Alpha is not a licensed securities dealer, broker or US investment adviser or investment bank. Our analysts are third party authors that include both professional investors and individual investors who may not be licensed or certified by any institute or regulatory body.</span></p> <p class=\"MsoNoSpacing\"> </p> <div class=\"before_last_paragraph-piano-placeholder\"></div> <p class=\"MsoNormal\"><b><span></span></b></p> <div class=\"sa-art article-width paywall-full-content\" id=\"a-body\"><span class=\"content-end p p1\"></span></div>", "image": null, "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4740932-politics-and-the-markets-120324", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 08:00:00"}, {"id": "4741631", "title": "ISM Manufacturing Index Higher Than Last Month", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488573364/image_1488573364.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Engineer And Manager Walking And Talking In Warehouse\" data-id=\"1488573364\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1025px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488573364/image_1488573364.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488573364/image_1488573364.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488573364/image_1488573364.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488573364/image_1488573364.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488573364/image_1488573364.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488573364/image_1488573364.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488573364/image_1488573364.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488573364/image_1488573364.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Tom Werner</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>By Jennifer Nash</em></p> <p>The Institute for Supply Management (ISM) manufacturing purchasing managers' index (PMI) increased to 48.4 in November but remains in contraction territory for an eighth straight month. The index has now contracted for 24 of the past 25 months. The latest reading</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1488573364/image_1488573364.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741631-ism-manufacturing-index-higher-than-last-month", "pub_date": "2024-12-03 07:45:00"}, {"id": "4741628", "title": "Top 50 High Quality Dividend Growth Stocks - November 2024", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484268315/image_1484268315.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Businessman holding glowing virtual technical graph and chart for analysis stock market in 2024, technology investment and value investment concept.\" data-id=\"1484268315\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"895px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484268315/image_1484268315.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484268315/image_1484268315.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484268315/image_1484268315.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484268315/image_1484268315.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484268315/image_1484268315.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1484268315/image_1484268315.jpg?io=getty